text: Prosopocera mediomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1938.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera mediomaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1938
